OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy, cold and wet start to
OL,6,Fthe day. Outbreaks of rain continuing
OL,7,Ffor many through the morning, with
OL,8,Fsome hill snow in the north. Drier for
OL,9,Fthe afternoon, but remaining cloudy.
OL,10,FFeeling colder than Thursday.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FIt will remain mostly dry
OL,13,Fthough this evening and overnight,
OL,14,Fthough often on the cloudy side.
OL,15,FTurning chilly where any cloud breaks
OL,16,Foccur, with perhaps a few fog patches.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
