OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA cloudy morning, with
OL,6,Fpatchy rain over the hills. A few
OL,7,Fbrighter breaks are possible during
OL,8,Fthe afternoon, though further patchy
OL,9,Frain may also develop. Feeling a
OL,10,Flittle milder.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FThe
OL,13,Fcloudy theme will continue. It will be
OL,14,Fmostly dry, but some showery rain is
OL,15,Fpossible at times. Feeling mild where
OL,16,Fthe cloud breaks and the sun comes out.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
